    "description": "准备好乘坐惊险刺激的电梯，穿过机器人出没的塔楼吧。运用强大的魔法和杂技动作，从一群机械恶魔手中夺回炼金师的领地。<br><br>这款快节奏的冒险游戏是备受赞誉的Savant - Ascent的续作，你将踏上节节攀升的新道路！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/dee3f5740fa30cf638987017ccac2f39.poster.avif?t=1733728427\" width=618 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/dee3f5740fa30cf638987017ccac2f39.webm?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/dee3f5740fa30cf638987017ccac2f39.mp4?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>迎接每个关卡的独特挑战，迎战全新的敌人和强大的头目！对抗议会，迎战激光鲨鱼！你身处地下墓穴的黑暗之中，这可是难以捉摸的瓦尔炼金师的巢穴！在灿烂的星空下与入侵者战斗，最后对抗终极对手——不朽武士！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/26446c88a0da2a40fe4e3f5066671cbb.poster.avif?t=1733728427\" width=620 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/26446c88a0da2a40fe4e3f5066671cbb.webm?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/26446c88a0da2a40fe4e3f5066671cbb.mp4?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>跌宕起伏的双摇杆射击游戏，可在两个平台之间跳跃或冲刺来避免敌人的攻击，或调整自己的位置来获得完美的射击。<br></li><li>填满能量条，并用爆炸魔法轰炸敌人。<br></li><li>节节攀升时，获取充能道具以提升技能。解锁音乐艺术家Savant创作的奖励曲目。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/1e390fd60a2f41bd1dbac68877def602.poster.avif?t=1733728427\" width=618 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/1e390fd60a2f41bd1dbac68877def602.webm?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/1e390fd60a2f41bd1dbac68877def602.mp4?t=1733728427\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>多种游戏模式：<br><br>正常模式：按照自己的节奏征服塔楼。每个关卡之间以及遇到每个头目前，都设有检查点。节节攀升时，你会获得额外的生命。<br><br>硬核模式：面临更大的挑战。掌握你可以使用的技能，并一次性完成所有关卡——没有检查点，也没有额外的生命。<br><br>生存模式：争分夺秒地战斗。敌人的数量还会比以前更多，头目会自行出现，而你要竭尽所能地活下来。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/583bed5ad9ab85414ce32b6d884f8fea.avif?t=1733728427\" width=620 height=226 /></span><br><br>在Savant - Ascent REMIX中，体验前所未有的音乐艺术家的奇幻世界，将于9月15日登陆Steam。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279330/extras/e29b675eac308dfde3d286d7ae32f503.avif?t=1733728427\" width=620 height=620 /></span>",
